<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) in the instruments which it adopts, the Council has to confer on the Commission powers for the implementation of the rules which the Council lays down; the Council may impose certain requirements in respect of the exercise of these powers; it may also reserve to itself the right, in specific and substantiated cases, to exercise directly implementing powers; </inglise>
