<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The choice of procedural methods for the adoption of implementing measures shall be guided by the following criteria: </inglise>
<eesti> Rakendusmeetmete vastuv&otilde;tmisel kasutatava menetluse valik p&otilde;hineb j&auml;rgmistel kriteeriumidel: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) management measures, such as those relating to the application of the common agricultural and common fisheries policies, or to the implementation of programmes with substantial budgetary implications, should be adopted by use of the management procedure; </inglise>
<eesti> a) korralduskomitee menetlust kasutades tuleks vastu v&otilde;tta korraldusmeetmed, n&auml;iteks sellised, mis on seotud &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika ja &uuml;hise kalanduspoliitika rakendamisega v&otilde;i oluliselt eelarvet m&otilde;jutavate programmide rakendamisega; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) measures of general scope designed to apply essential provisions of basic instruments, including measures concerning the protection of the health or safety of humans, animals or plants, should be adopted by use of the regulatory procedure; where a basic instrument stipulates that certain non-essential provisions of the instrument may be adapted or updated by way of implementing procedures, such measures should be adopted by use of the regulatory procedure; </inglise>
<eesti> b) regulatiivkomitee menetlust kasutades tuleks vastu v&otilde;tta &uuml;ldmeetmed, mis on m&otilde;eldud rakendama p&otilde;hiaktide olulisi s&auml;tteid, kaasa arvatud meetmed, mis k&auml;sitlevad inimeste, loomade ja taimede tervise ja ohutuse kaitset; kui p&otilde;hiakt n&auml;eb ette, et selle teatavaid v&auml;hemolulisi s&auml;tteid v&otilde;ib kohandada v&otilde;i ajakohastada rakendusmenetlusega, tuleks sellised meetmed vastu v&otilde;tta regulatiivkomitee menetlust kasutades; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) without prejudice to points (a) and (b), the advisory procedure shall be used in any case in which it is considered to be the most appropriate. </inglise>
<eesti> c) n&otilde;uandemenetlust kasutatakse alati, kui seda peetakse k&otilde;ige sobivamaks, ilma et see piiraks punktide a ja b kohaldamist. </eesti>
